Deploying a Dockerized Vue.js Application to AWS ECS using GitHub Actions CI/CD Pipeline.

The candidate will:

- Build a basic Vue.js app.
- Create a Docker image of the app.
- Push the image to AWS ECR.
- Deploy the containerized app to AWS ECS.
- Automate this entire workflow using GitHub Actions.

You can present it like this:

Task Subject: CI/CD for a Dockerized Frontend App
Goal: Set up a full CI/CD pipeline to build and deploy a Vue.js web application to AWS ECS via GitHub Actions.
